Description: Raspberry Pi PiSP ISP userspace library (unofficial Ubuntu build)
 Userspace driver for the Raspberry Pi 5's PiSP (Pi Image Signal Processor)
 hardware block. Provides the runtime support that the rpi/pisp pipeline
 handler in libcamera links against to drive the ISP — debayering, AE/AWB,
 lens shading correction, denoise — in silicon rather than on the CPU.
 .
 This is an unofficial rebuild of the upstream sources for Ubuntu on Raspberry
 Pi 5. Not provided or endorsed by Raspberry Pi Ltd.
